    "When indexing differences to November 2022, the difference-in-differences estimates in Panel (b) show no differential changes for adopters following the introduction of AI chatbots.",
    "The estimates remain flat even among adopters whose employers explicitly encourage chatbot use.",
    "Appendix E.2.1 shows that these null results hold separately for workers' hourly wages, intensive-margin hours, and extensive-margin employment.",
